# Architecture

## Directory Structure

```text
src/
├── app/(public)/          # login, register, forgot-password
├── app/(private)/         # dashboard, transactions, categories, setting
├── api/                   # REST service layer
├── components/[name]/     # index.tsx + hooks.ts
├── components/ui/         # Shadcn atomic UI
├── hooks/                 # Global hooks only
├── lib/                   # axios, utils
├── types/                 # Response<T>, shared types
└── utils/helpers/         # Pure utility functions
```

## Path Aliases

Cross-directory imports MUST use `@/*` aliases. Never use `../../`.

| Alias | Target |
|-------|--------|
| `@/api/*` | `src/api/*` |
| `@/components/*` | `src/components/*` |
| `@/ui/*` | `src/components/ui/*` |
| `@/hooks/*` | `src/hooks/*` |
| `@/types/*` | `src/types/*` |
| `@/lib/*` | `src/lib/*` |
| `@/store/*` | `src/store/*` |
| `@/helpers/*` | `src/utils/helpers/*` |

Same-directory imports use relative paths (e.g. `./hooks`).

Full reference: `docs/coding-standards.md`
